This is the birth record for Henry Clegg and it matches the information in the tree.
This 1880 Census shows the names of both Henry's wives, all children from both wives; it is interesting that both of his families lived in one home.  That takes great faith on the part of both wives.
Source for the pioneer company he traveled with.
There is a photo of Henry Clegg on pg. 428, and a short bio of him on pg. 811.
Source that Henry Clegg is the father of Herbert Lorenzo Clegg.
